== Награды ==
Осаму Тэдзука за свои работы удостоился многих премий и наград{{sfn|MacWilliams|2008|p=35}}{{sfn|Onoda Power|2009|p=4}}, среди которых [[орден Священного Сокровища]], [[премия манги Shogakukan]], [[премия манги Коданся]].

* 1958 год — премия манги Shogakukan за манги Manga Seminar on Biology и Biiko-chan<ref name="shogakuganaward">{{cite web|url = http://comics.shogakukan.co.jp/mangasho/rist.html|title = 小学館漫画賞: 歴代受賞者|author = |date = |work = |publisher = ''[[Shogakukan]]''|accessdate = 2015-05-30|lang=ja}}</ref><ref name ="teznet1950">{{cite web|url = http://tezukaosamu.net/en/about/1950.html|title = About Tezuka Osamu > History > 1950s|author = |date = |work = |publisher = ''tezukaosamu.net''|accessdate = 2015-05-30|lang=en}}</ref>
* 1967 год — премия Офудзи Нобуро за аниме Tenrankai no E<ref name ="teznet1960"/>
* 1977 год — премия манги Коданся за манги [[Black Jack (манга)|Black Jack]] и [[Mitsume ga Tooru (манга)|Mitsume ga Tooru]]<ref name=" kodanshaaward">{{cite web|url = http://www.hahnlibrary.net/comics/awards/kodansha.shtml|title = Kodansha Manga Award|author = |date = |work = |publisher = ''Comic Book Awards Almanac''|accessdate = 2015-05-30|lang=en|archiveurl = http://web.archive.org/web/20070816031310/http://www.hahnlibrary.net/comics/awards/kodansha.shtml|archivedate = 2007-08-16}}</ref>
* 1984 год — премия манги Shogakukan за мангу Hidamari no Ki<ref name="shogakuganaward"/><ref>{{cite web|url = http://tezukaosamu.net/en/about/1980.html|title = About Tezuka Osamu > History > 1980s|author = |date = |work = |publisher = ''tezukaosamu.net''|accessdate = 2015-05-30|lang=en}}</ref>
* 1986 год — премия манги Коданся за мангу [[Adolf Ni Tsugu]]<ref name=" kodanshaaward"/>
* 1989 год — орден Священного Сокровища (посмертно)<ref>{{cite web|url = http://www.hagiomoto.net/news/2012/04/post-94.html|title = 萩尾望都先生が紫綬褒章を受章|author = |date = |work = |publisher = ''hagiomoto.net''|accessdate = 2015-06-13|lang=ja}}</ref>
* 1990 год — премия Министерства образования Японии{{sfn|MacWilliams|2008|p=44}}<ref>{{cite web|url = https://tezukaosamu.net/en/productions/trans.html|title = TEZUKA Osamu and Tezuka Productions|author = |date = |work = |publisher = ''tezukaosamu.net''|accessdate = 2015-06-28|lang=en}}</ref>
* 2004 год — [[премия Айснера]] за мангу Buddha<ref>{{cite web|url = http://www.hahnlibrary.net/comics/awards/eisner04.php|title = 2004 Will Eisner Comic Industry Awards|author = |date = |work = |publisher = ''Comic Book Awards Almanac''|accessdate = 2015-05-30|lang=en|archiveurl = http://web.archive.org/web/20120207060154/http://www.hahnlibrary.net/comics/awards/eisner04.php|archivedate = 2012-02-07}}</ref>
* 2005 год — премия Айснера за мангу Buddha<ref>{{cite web|url = http://www.hahnlibrary.net/comics/awards/eisner05.php|title = 2005 Will Eisner Comic Industry Awards|author = |date = |work = |publisher = ''Comic Book Awards Almanac''|accessdate = 2015-05-30|lang=en|archiveurl = http://web.archive.org/web/20120207060456/http://www.hahnlibrary.net/comics/awards/eisner05.php|archivedate = 2012-02-07}}</ref>
